  T 1 get R 5 get mul
  add
  T 2 get R 8 get mul
  add
  
  T 3 get
  
  % second row
  T 4 get R 0 get mul
  T 5 get R 3 get mul
  add
  T 6 get R 6 get mul
  add
  
  T 4 get R 1 get mul
  T 5 get R 4 get mul
  add
  T 6 get R 7 get mul
  add
  
  T 4 get R 2 get mul
  T 5 get R 5 get mul
  add
  T 6 get R 8 get mul
  add
  
  T 7 get
  
  % third row
  T 8 get R 0 get mul
