% but the vector is a linear function

/dual-transform3d { 4 dict begin
/v exch def
/T exch def
[
  v 0 get T 0 get mul
  v 1 get T 4 get mul add
  v 2 get T 8 get mul add
  v 3 get T 12 get mul add
  
