% sx sy sz

/scale3d {
8 dict begin
/sz exch def
/sy exch def
/sx exch def
/T cgfx3d 0 get def
[
[
  T 0 get sx mul
  T 1 get sy mul
  T 2 get sz mul
  T 3 get 
  
  T 4 get sx mul
  T 5 get sy mul
  T 6 get sz mul
  T 7 get 
  
  T 8 get sx mul
  T 9 get sy mul
  T 10 get sz mul
  T 11 get 
 
  T 12 get sx mul
  T 13 get sy mul
  T 14 get sz mul
  T 15 get 
]
/T cgfx3d 1 get def
